Name: New York Mortgage Trust, Inc. 9.125% Senior Notes Due 2029
Description: New York Mortgage Trust, Inc. (ticker: ADAMI) is a real estate investment trust (REIT) that specializes in investing, financing, and managing a diverse portfolio of mortgage-related assets, including both agency and non-agency mortgage-backed securities. The company is dedicated to maximizing returns for stakeholders by strategically targeting high-yield investments while maintaining a robust balance sheet. With its 9.125% Senior Notes due 2029, ADAMI offers institutional investors an attractive opportunity for stable income distribution, coupled with its commitment to delivering favorable risk-adjusted returns amidst evolving market conditions.
